    "description": "<strong>------------ About the game ------------</strong><br>Control Suzu, the cat-eared girl, and work with her partner, Mari, the ghost cat, to reach the goal!<br><br>Throw Mari to possess ghost in the stage.<br>You can freely control the possessed ghost as a player character.<br><br>The possessed ghost can be used as a scaffold, push switches, use its unique abilities, and more.<br>Use them to your advantage to solve the stage's tricks and open the way to the goal.<br><br>Try your best to clear all 60+ stages of the puzzle!<br><br><br><strong>------------ Game Rules ------------</strong><br>This game is an orthodox 2D action puzzle game that uses only the left/right move, jump, and possession buttons.<br><br>The player controls Suzu, the player character, and uses the possession and gimmicks to her advantage.<br>The goal of the game is to reach the goal point bell.<br><br><br><strong>------------ Operation ------------</strong><br># Keyboard<br>Arrow keys : Select menu / Move<br>Space key : Jump<br>Z key : Decide / Activate possession / Release possession<br>X key : Cancel<br>Esc : Pause<br><br># Gamepad<br>Cross key : Select menu / Move<br>0 button : Decide / Jump<br>1 button : Cancel / Activate possession / Release possession<br>7 button : Pause<br>* Gamepad key assignments can be changed from the options menu.",
